OL,3,CRemainder of Isle of Man TT cancelled
OL,4,Cafter bad weather halts racing
OL,6,FThe remainder of the Isle of Man TT
OL,7,Fhas been cancelled after poor weather
OL,8,Fstopped racing.
OL,10,FRace organisers say the fortnight has
OL,11,Fbeen "one of the most challenging" for
OL,12,Fweather conditions and, after a
OL,13,Fconsultation between the Clerk of the
OL,14,FCourt and the Isle of Man Met Office,
OL,15,Fthere would not be enough time to
OL,16,Fsafely complete further racing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
