FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780851960
OL,3,CRemainder of Isle of Man TT cancelled
OL,4,Cafter bad weather halts racing
OL,6,FRain has affected seven of the nine
OL,7,Fracing days, and with conditions
OL,8,Faround the course "not looking to
OL,9,Fsufficiently improve within the
OL,10,Frequired time", the decision was made
OL,11,Fto cancel the remainder of the event.
OL,13,FIt means the Senior TT result has been
OL,14,Fdeclared based on the positions at the
OL,15,Fend of lap one - with Dean Harrison
OL,16,Fcrowned the winner.
OL,18,FPeter Hickman has been awarded second
OL,19,Fplace, while Josh Brookes came in
OL,20,Fthird.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
