CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780851960
OL,3,CRemainder of Isle of Man TT cancelled
OL,4,Cafter bad weather halts racing
OL,6,FThe Sportbike TT Race 2 has been
OL,7,Fcancelled and will not take place.
OL,9,FClerk of the Course Gary Thompson MBE
OL,10,FBEM said: "This has undoubtedly been
OL,11,Fone of the most challenging TTs in
OL,12,Frecent years from a weather
OL,13,Fperspective.
OL,26,@rD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780851960
OL,3,CRemainder of Isle of Man TT cancelled
OL,4,Cafter bad weather halts racing
OL,6,F"Over the course of the event, we set
OL,7,Fout with nine days on which racing
OL,8,Fcould potentially have taken place,
OL,9,Fand rain will have affected seven of
OL,10,Fthem. That is an exceptional set of
OL,11,Fcircumstances and it has had a major
OL,12,Fimpact on what we have been able to
OL,13,Fdeliver.
OL,15,F"Throughout the event, the weather
OL,16,Fsimply hasn't worked in our favour. We
OL,17,Fhave faced low cloud, rain, standing
OL,18,Fwater and changing conditions across
OL,19,Fdifferent parts of the Mountain
OL,20,FCourse, which have significantly
OL,21,Flimited the windows available to us.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780851961
OL,3,CRemainder of Isle of Man TT cancelled
OL,4,Cafter bad weather halts racing
OL,6,F"We fully appreciate that today's
OL,7,Foutcome will be disappointing for
OL,8,Fcompetitors, teams, sponsors,
OL,9,Fvolunteers and, of course, the
OL,10,Fthousands of fans who travel to the
OL,11,FIsle of Man from around the world to
OL,12,Fexperience the TT.
OL,14,F"However, throughout the event we have
OL,15,Fremained committed to making the very
OL,16,Fbest use of every available weather
OL,17,Fwindow, while carefully managing the
OL,18,Foperational, logistical and safety
OL,19,Fconsiderations involved in delivering
OL,20,Fracing on the Mountain Course.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780851961
OL,3,CRemainder of Isle of Man TT cancelled
OL,4,Cafter bad weather halts racing
OL,6,F"The challenges we have faced this
OL,7,Fyear are part of the nature of an
OL,8,Fevent that takes place on 37.73 miles
OL,9,Fof public roads. That is what makes
OL,10,Fthe TT unique, but it also means that
OL,11,Fweather and course conditions will
OL,12,Falways play a significant role in
OL,13,Fdetermining what is possible.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
