OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780851961
OL,3,CRemainder of Isle of Man TT cancelled
OL,4,Cafter bad weather halts racing
OL,6,F"I would like to sincerely thank our
OL,7,Fcompetitors, teams, marshals,
OL,8,Fvolunteers, officials, medical teams,
OL,9,Fresidents, partners and fans for their
OL,10,Fpatience, understanding and continued
OL,11,Fsupport throughout what has been a
OL,12,Fdifficult week. Their cooperation has
OL,13,Fbeen greatly appreciated."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
